{"tid":818331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭抱怨急難救助不力 大阪辦事處長蘇啟誠輕生亡","createTime":"2018-09-14T04:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T10:25:36.000Z","uid":37554,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa44153cba59251b437e780083eb4ddd069e474","tid":818331,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"外交部今天證實，駐大阪辦事處處長蘇啟誠清晨於大阪官邸輕生，外交部對此一不幸事件表達最深切的悲痛及惋惜。蘇啟誠7月才剛上任，今天上午在寓所被人發現疑似上吊身亡，駐日代表謝長廷聞訊已趕往大阪瞭解情況。<br />\n<br />\n本關西機場日前受颱風重創一度關閉，許多台灣旅客受困，駐大阪辦事處遭抱怨未提供妥善協助。<br />\n<br />\n外交部證實，蘇啟誠今天清晨於官邸輕生。外交部表示，蘇啟誠處事認真負責，擔任外交人員生涯期間表現優異，外交部對於蘇啟誠不幸離開，表達最深摯的沈痛與不捨。外交部將全力協助家屬處理後續事宜，也期盼社會各界尊重家屬的隱私與心情。<br />\n<br />\n蘇啓誠出身私立東吳大學日本語學系、中國文化大學日本語文學研究所外，也曾到國立大阪大學日本語學研究科讀書，在1991年進入外交部服務後，2007成為駐日本代表處秘書，2013年成為駐那霸辦事處處長，今年7月調到大阪，單身赴任。<br />\n<br />\n據消息人士說，蘇啟誠今天沒有如常到辦事處上班，祕書前往他的寓所查看時，發現他似乎是上吊輕生，已經沒有生命跡象。<br />\n<br />\n政府駐日6個館處的主管，原定明天要在大阪召開會議，議程包括檢討最近關西機場受颱風侵襲時，駐日官員因應台灣旅客受困的作為。"},{"pid":"3a116ce347c938676913ceb5cb6c4f48827e269e","tid":818331,"uid":95,"like":47,"dislike":8,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"若果香港班垃圾有日本一成就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485acde72351ab5452e8741fb97871d805728a9d","tid":818331,"uid":2772,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"馬時享學到佢一半就好<br />\n<br />\n起碼都半身不遂"},{"pid":"be87d4924f64bff1ecba25907b8d16e7c79c416e","tid":818331,"uid":26770,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"呢D咪擔當<br />\n<br />\n正如當日日本賣毒米食壞人的米商自殺向人民問責<br />\n而當日支持起高鐵班藍絲香港人扮傻當無事<br />\n<br />\n文化絕對有高低"},{"pid":"8aef8d4c2d47f39ba84c4356dad00fde449887e6","tid":818331,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  讀好他的工作態度"},{"pid":"7ca8d0c57aede005b4681894601fe45e2b3d0a90","tid":818331,"uid":109462,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">綠營人士強調，大家都在罵謝長廷，但此次問題最大的還是在大阪辦事處長身上，卻沒人知道處長是誰</span></strong>，況且謝身為駐日代表根本管不到這麼細，也管不到大阪轄區，除非辦事處長改成政務任用，駐外代表有全權考核辦事處人員權力，才能權責相符，否則不管由誰來做都是背黑鍋。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民進黨立委蔡適應則認為</span></strong>，台灣長期來台日關係是長期重要一環，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這次淹水地區是大阪辦事處轄區，如同謝說，大阪末梢神經慢半拍，讓民眾詬病</span></strong>，相較之下札幌辦事處人員就較為認真，不過民眾不滿情緒也是鞭策政府原動力，相關單位需要檢討改進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3357302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3357302&d=9n63ACnIhs93NpSLY7Y4xy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2f0169d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3357302</a><br />\n<br />\n「下屬的功績是上司的功勞，上司的過錯是下屬的責任」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca0b6d04538ad88addda5e347be10421ce3eec5","tid":818331,"uid":11805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"2018年都見到切腹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b87a717b97ee85e28779faea0b269c455ad5eb","tid":818331,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"香港班狗官都未死啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大阪及北海道香港旅客水深火熱 <br />\n駐東京香港經濟貿易文化事務處係鹿兒島大魚大肉</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/809329/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/809329/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201809/05/P2018090400668_photo_1142773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201809%2F05%2FP2018090400668_photo_1142773.jpg&h=d1633d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201809/05/P2018090400668_photo_1142774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201809%2F05%2FP2018090400668_photo_1142774.jpg&h=dba63450&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dafb8824650d9fd7a30f87aced882bc26cdcc16","tid":818331,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"大陸香港完全唔好咁做"},{"pid":"f6a7aa8bad959e94fcc2e4efa35c0421d3ff6a52","tid":818331,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dafb8824650d9fd7a30f87aced882bc26cdcc16","tid":818331,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"大陸香港完全唔好咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"大陸香港官員完全唔會咁做"},{"pid":"2fe765e9bc5f4b0879acdfab772479545e0996af","tid":818331,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0dafb8824650d9fd7a30f87aced882bc26cdcc16","tid":818331,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"大陸香港完全唔好咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"實會變無政府狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ffe433442470a1bb21a743401a85330f4706f9","tid":818331,"uid":95,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"485acde72351ab5452e8741fb97871d805728a9d","tid":818331,"uid":2772,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"馬時享學到佢一半就好<br />\n<br />\n起碼都半身不遂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"最好長命百歲百病纏身"},{"pid":"b74701daaed9a3cda6b1f418163c1f82bf906cc1","tid":818331,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces